Texts.Eng: Floran needs sssturdier clothes. These couldn't survive a hunt at all!
Texts.Chs: 叶族人需要更结实的衣服。这些根本无法在狩猎中生存！

Texts.Eng: Hm... This shirt is lovely, but it's dry clean only...
Texts.Chs: 嗯。。。这件衬衫很漂亮，但它只能干洗。。。

Texts.Eng: I've yet to find shoes anywhere that are easy on my talons...
Texts.Chs: 我还没有在任何地方找到我的爪子容易穿的鞋子。。。

Texts.Eng: Makeover, makeover, makeover, makeover, makeover, makeover - MAKEOVER!
Texts.Chs: 改造，改造，改造，改造，改造，改造，改造-改造！

Texts.Eng: Must these tags always itch when I'm trying clothes on? I shouldn't even NEED to itch!
Texts.Chs: 我试穿衣服时，这些标签一定会痒吗？我甚至不需要痒！

Texts.Eng: That's quite the price tag... I think I'll stick with my own duds, thanks.
Texts.Chs: 这正是价格标签。。。我想我还是用我自己的衣服吧，谢谢。

Texts.Eng: These are all a bit too small for me...
Texts.Chs: 这些对我来说都有点太小了。。。

Texts.Eng: This calls for a dress up montage!
Texts.Chs: 这需要一个化妆蒙太奇！
